558
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:40,320
I might.

559
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:43,160
I could watch you play jazz.

560
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,480
That sounds quite romantic.

561
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,640
