562
00:39:50,800 --> 00:39:52,680
You wanted me to tune your guitar, right?

563
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:10,120
You're growing up fast, huh?

564
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:14,920
Back then,
I was the one tuning your guitar.

565
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:20,560
You can do it yourself,

566
