571
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:42,080
- Duang?
- Yes?

572
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:44,040
Do you like desserts?

573
00:40:44,160 --> 00:40:46,000
Oh, I can eat them.

574
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:47,800
I've been eating tons
hanging out with Qin.

575
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,400
He absolutely loves desserts.

576
00:40:49,520 --> 00:40:51,840
He got that from me.

577
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,920
- Oh, he does?
- Mm.

578
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:57,640
I used to buy him lots of desserts,

579
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:59,160
and when he noms...

580
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,120
Uh...

581
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:03,280
I mean, when he eats,

582
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:05,320
he looks adorable.

583
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:15,340
I'm glad that you opened up to Duang,

584
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:19,520
