585
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:27,120
Even though you haven't played
this guitar for a long time,

586
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,680
it's still working just fine.

587
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:37,240
I'll go see Duang now.

588
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:53,120
Qin is quiet and not so good with words.

589
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,200
Please be patient with him.

590
00:41:56,200 --> 00:41:57,320
Of course.

591
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:01,400
Qin might seem stern,

592
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,280
but he's actually the cutest.

593
00:42:03,620 --> 00:42:05,020
He gives me peace of mind.

594
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:08,160
Stern...

595
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:11,080
Did I say something wrong?

596
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:13,240
No, not at all.

597
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,600
The reason he seems that way
is probably because of...

598
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:19,920
his dad and me.

599
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:24,840
Back then,

600
00:42:25,300 --> 00:42:28,480
