601
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:31,680
I guess that's why
he doesn't want to be home with us.

602
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,360
You're annoying!

603
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:42,800
I told you to shut up!

604
00:42:52,080 --> 00:42:53,360
I thought...

605
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:56,760
Qin wouldn't probably
remember those things.

606
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:59,080
But it's indelible for his dad and me,

607
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:02,240
