brought this up to him ever again.

608
00:43:08,480 --> 00:43:09,560
I understand.

609
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:13,160
Qin has been through a lot.

610
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:16,000
I only want the best for him.

611
00:43:16,920 --> 00:43:18,480
He's always been strong, though.

612
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:22,920
I sometimes wish I could be half as strong,

613
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:29,920
