trust you with my heart, Duang.

690
00:51:45,720 --> 00:51:49,410
♫Who'd believe that, from the start,♫

691
00:51:49,580 --> 00:51:53,540
♫I fell for you with all my heart,♫

692
00:51:53,680 --> 00:52:00,680
